{"title":"安全在哪儿？","authors":["池北偶　苗地"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":12,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗　苗地画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西贡美军宿舍被炸毁后，美国侵略者惊惶不安，悲叹在南越哪里都没有安全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每寸土浸透仇恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每双眼冒着火花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波来梅固然危险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西贡市同样可怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军声东击西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游击队神通广大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他打得着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你找不到他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出门挨打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呆着挨炸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘坦克碰着地雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐飞机被枪打下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商贩能扔炸弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和尚也会刺杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩子袖藏尖刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘善打活靶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用不着怨天怨地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用不着喊爹喊妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里没有安全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处都是绞架。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要想保住性命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有滚回老家！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}